data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home, nestled on a spacious corner lot. As you step inside, you'll find a versatile den/office space awaiting your finishing touches. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts an oversized pantry perfect for storing all your food and large appliances.  Venture outside and you're greeted by a serene backyard enveloped with a wooded privacy fence - an ideal setting for tranquil summer evenings or hosting gatherings with loved ones. For those cold winter days, rest easy knowing your vehicle is protected in the single-car garage, which also offers ample storage space.  Benefit from the property's prime location, minutes away from shopping centers, dining options, and schools.  Don't let this gem slip through your fingers. Schedule your viewing today and make this house yours forever. Hurry, as properties like this don't linger on the market for long!
